descript.abstract: This dataset is a statewide compilation of California's Marine Life Protection Act (MLPA) Study Regions.
descript.purpose: Study Regions aid in the planning of California's MLPA Initiative process.
descript.supplinf: This dataset is a merge of the five individual MLPA Study Region datasets: BAS_NCSR, BAS_NCCSR, BAS_SFBSR, BAS_CCSR, and BAS_SCSR. Where the individual BAS_CCSR dataset overlapped with the BAS_SCSR, the BAS_SCSR took precendence and the overlapping area erased from the BAS_CCSR dataset. Where the individual BAS_NCCSR dataset overlapped with the BAS_NCSR, the BAS_NCSR took precendence and overlapping area erased from the BAS_NCCSR dataset.
